features: ​Hey, howdy, hey! This Roundup Fun Woody doll from Disney and Pixar's Toy Story brings home the adventure and friendships of the movies. Just pull the tab on his back to hear 30+ phrases.

​Woody returns to his roots as a rag doll with a soft body, iconic western outfit made from fabric, and molded plastic head, hat, boots, belt and hands. This Woody figure is ready for an authentic round-up of fun!
​At 12.25 inches tall, this classic toy is ready to be every kid's best friend and travel along on adventures near and far. Thanks to deputies like you, the wild west is safe!
​With a collection of large scale figures to choose from, some with special features and accessories, kids can enjoy BIG playtime possibilities! Each sold separately and subject to availability.
​Makes a great movie-themed gift for Pixar fans ages 3 years and up, especially Toy Story fans!
body.description: This Roundup Fun Woody 12-inch figure will bring big realistic thrills to fans of the friendly sheriff from Disney and Pixar's Toy Story movies. His 30+ phrases are activated by the short pull-tab on his back. His movie-authentic look includes a soft rag doll body, iconic western shirt, jeans and vest, produced in fabric, and head, hat, boots, belt and hands made of plastic. Kids can relive all their favorite Woody scenes from the movie series, with the phrases coming directly from this talking Woody figure. Talking is activated by a short tab that is pulled, not an actual long pull string. Colors and decorations may vary.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: About Us Mattel is a global toy company and owner of one of the strong catalogs of children’s and family entertainment franchises in the world. They empower the next generation to explore the wonder of childhood and reach their full potential. They create innovative products and experiences that inspire, entertain and develop children through play. Their products are designed and developed to meet the applicable safety standards and are constructed with consumer safety in mind. When parents and families choose to buy their products, they can be assured that the safety and well being of their children is a top priority.

Disney Pixar Toy Story Roundup Fun Woody Large Talking Figure, 12 Inch This Roundup Fun Woody 12 inch figure will bring big realistic thrills to fans of the friendly sheriff from Disney and Pixar's Toy Story movies. With 30 plus phrases activated by the pull tab on his back, fans young and old can discover huge interactive fun. A sheriff always needs his deputy. His truly movie authentic look is achieved with multiple materials to really bring the character to life, including a soft rag doll body, iconic western shirt, jeans and vest, produced in fabric, and head, hat, boots, belt and hands made of plastic. Kids can relive all their favorite Woody scenes from the movie series, with the phrases coming directly from this talking Woody figure.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great looking Woody! NOT as pictured.
reviews.reviewText: Regarding the photos in this product image --- NOT ACCURATE. If you want the Woody shown in the first 5 photos, this is not it. I love when pages do that. The accurate product you're getting is the Woody shown in the box, with his mouth open slightly. He looks pretty good though. I searched for some time to find a Woody doll that looked the most like the movie, as some of them have some pretty creepy faces and are too cartoony. It seems like it should be pretty easy to recreate but apparently it is not. This one is quite close, though.Yes, his voice is clearly not Tom Hanks, but it's not TOO far off, honestly.My 4 and 1 year old both love him so much and he seems plenty durable so far! The "pull string" which doesn't really pull hasn't broken and is fun for both of them.
